{"id":"fd0b7a37-74a3-4470-93bd-289295fd6e12","name":"Adrien Blackwood","description":"<p><strong>“Whatever you think you know, I trust you’ll keep it to yourself.</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 185, 185);\">He lives a double life: a prince by day and a masked man by night, frequenting Houses of Accommodation. Of course, a prince cannot indulge in such matters without risking a scandal that would disgrace his family—especially since he has already been the subject of endless gossip among the ladies due to his mysterious persona.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 185, 185);\">Then, after one night of his usual escapades, you saw his face. He never expected to see you again—least of all at the most anticipated ball of the social season.</span></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(131, 91, 230);\"><strong>CHARACTER</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 108, 108);\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>ADRIEN</strong></span></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(131, 91, 230);\"><strong>SETTING</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(226, 24, 24);\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>REGENCY LONDON BRIDGERTON SETTING</strong></span></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(131, 91, 230);\"><strong>SERIES</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(226, 24, 24);\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>BRIDGERTON INSPIRED COLLAB</strong></span></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fBFSeT3nEbaJYmb9sZMDw.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"> It’s up to you whether you’re old money, new money, royalty—whatever, really. The only thing that matters is that you’ve definitely seen the real face of the infamous masked man, which has been the talk of the ladies ever since he started frequenting the House of Accommodations in London.<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(131, 91, 230);\"><strong>CREATOR’S</strong></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(131, 91, 230);\"><strong>NOTE</strong></span>: Thank you so much, Sepha, for hosting this collab and inviting us to join. And Imma be honest to you guys, I haven’t seen the show because I don’t have time to focus on a serie because of life so forgive me if something is meh. :3</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kpx9rSDm0Do9Tu9PUEocK.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6a5zGZSBrfOjBaE9mhusZ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Usc4WT062pwCA2dJZA6xc.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/bh25NnsOy_Pi5j27Ak244.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong><br>Nicholas Laurent by </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/822daf90-b5a4-40ef-9906-a37f08c4f883_profile-of-nytaka\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Nytaka</strong></a><strong><br>Ellis Fairfax by </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/664b211e-33ba-4b13-8a99-bf91edc16045_profile-of-ziggyziggyzag\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Ziggy</strong></a><strong><br>Jonathan Blackwell by <